"Your experience is an ASSET."

@MFSTEVE 

They don't have to be synonyms to work in a puzzle. An ASSET is always a positive thing. Whether it's a personal quality or an item of value, assets are inherently positive. 

Plus, I'm not  a finance expert but if your assets are greater in value than your liabilities, then you would be net positive.

